Good  writing  style  aside, I suspect
that  many  sceners will be »CL0:put off»CL1: by
the   style  and  theme  in  »CL6:Devotion»CL1:.
»CL6:Devotion»CL1:   isn't  »CL6: Buzz»CL1:,  a  mag  some
