but   the  impression  one  gets  when
reading »CL6:Devotion»CL1:, is a focusing on the
»CL0:old»CL1:  scene,  on  the  »CL0:old»CL1:  values,  on
everything   being   better  and  more
important  back then.  Old groups like
»CL2:Anarchy»CL1:,  »CL2: Sanity»CL1:,   etc.,  are  being
mentioned as rolemodels often, and the
