the  scene  was  in  the  past, BUT!..
This  is  not  something  to have as a
recurring  theme in an entire diskmag!
Not  »CL0:explicitly»CL1:  or »CL0:implicitly»CL1: stated.
It likely annoys the hell out of newer
sceners  (who  haven't been around for
10   years)   to   get  to  know  that
everything  was  much better then, and
sceners  more  skilled,  etc.   It  is
